   Used in: packages/frontend/synthesizer/libs/mpt/, packages/frontend/synthesizer/libs/util/
   Original source: https://github.com/ethereumjs/ethereumjs-monorepo
   
   These components retain their original MPL-2.0 license as required by the MPL-2.0
   license terms. See the LICENSE files in the respective directories.

2. ICICLE (Ingonyama ZK Acceleration Library)
   Copyright (c) Ingonyama
   Licensed under the MIT License
   
   Used in: packages/backend/
   Original source: https://github.com/ingonyama-zk/icicle

3. Arkworks (Cryptographic Libraries)
   Copyright (c) arkworks contributors
   Licensed under the Apache License 2.0 and MIT License
   
   Used in: packages/backend/
   Original source: https://github.com/arkworks-rs

4. Circom
   Copyright (c) iden3
   Licensed under the GNU General Public License v3.0
   
   Used as: Compile-time tool only (not linked at runtime)
   Original source: https://github.com/iden3/circom

5. Other Dependencies
   
   This software depends on numerous other open-source packages.
   Please see the package.json and Cargo.toml files in each package
   for a complete list of dependencies and their respective licenses.

